snippet: The veteran receiver Brian Hartline signed a five-year deal for nearly $31 million to remain with the Miami Dolphins, his agent said.
abstract: Miami Dolphins resign receiver Brian Hartline to five-year deal worth nearly $31 million.
lead_paragraph: The veteran receiver Brian Hartline signed a five-year deal for nearly $31 million to remain with the Miami Dolphins, his agent said.
